➜谁才是纸老虎？Model X跌出前十，600km续航大军再添两款国产车
http://www.sohu.com/a/411571442_115706	25120
<p><strong>电动车续航里程排名（7月）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200805/f4689979cec14feca16a600950ca71ec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200805/612c80b8cc174d29a8adb8ee4e06e57c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
